ðŸ§© Problem Solved: Leetcode 1903. Largest Odd Number in String
ðŸ”— Problem Link: https://lnkd.in/dUqsje3U

#include <string>
using namespace std;

class Solution {
public:
    string largestOddNumber(string num) {
        int n = num.size();
        
        // Iterate through the string from right to left
        for (int i = n - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
            // Check if the current digit is odd
            if ((num[i] - '0') % 2 != 0) {
                // If odd, return the substring from the beginning of the string up to the current index
                return num.substr(0, i + 1);
            }
        }

        // If no odd digit is found, return an empty string
        return "";
    }
};

The algorithm iterates through the string once from right to left, where 'n' is the length of the input string.
Time Complexity: O(n)

